{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 212.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember one little incident, maybe very foolish to even bring up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was this little man, this SS man, who, when he addressed us in order to give us direction and scare us a little bit before we marched out to our work, he stood up on a chair.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he belted out these threats to us because the-- for example, one day before this particular speech, we women were resting somewhere near an-- near a garden.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were-- there was an apple tree, and the branches were hanging over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The apples were ripe, so some of the women climbed up, two of them, three of them, climbed up and cleaned out that branch.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we all ate apples.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "First of all, it was German property.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Secondly, we were prisoners and had no right to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the way he billed it up, I fell apart laughing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was so comical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He looks outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] It means Jew women, not Jewish women, that is refined.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jew women is derogatory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jew women on the apple trees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had this picture suddenly in my mind of us Jew women growing out of-- of these trees and producing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought it was, here is this little man yelling at us to that we ate those apples.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these Jewish women on-- on-- growing out of the apple trees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just couldn't help laughing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother said, stop laughing, he'll see you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not worth it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm growing out of the pear tree this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it-- so we laughed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We did laugh.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
